1.Inside the express js to create get and post method:
example:
app.get('',()=>{});
app.post('',()=>{});

2.
How to send json data from backend to frontend;
example:
res.status().json({})
//Inside the json you can send the object and automatically in frontend it will be converted in json response.

3.How to access frontend body data in backend?
//we need to use req.body to access the data in backend
//we need to use body parser given by nodejs to parse and extract the data from frontend.
//So in backend you need to convert to json or object it will take care automatically.
